The publicly available MinXSS data can be accessed on the MinXSS website http://lasp.colorado.edu/home/minxss/. These data will include Level 0c, Level 0d, and Level 1 – 5 products, and one of the most relevant products will be the Level 1 spectral irradiance (photons s−1cm−2keV−1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
