				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}${<}\,1~\mbox{keV}$\end{document}).
MinXSS/X123 can only set upper limits on the emission measure and cannot definitively constrain the temperature values for dimmer plasma hotter than ≈5MK\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
