				\begin{document}${\approx}\,4.5~\mbox{MK}$\end{document} for energy bins lower than 3 keV and limited significant counts from energy bins greater than 3 keV. The latter is a consequence of the relatively small X123 aperture area (2.5×10−4cm2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
